1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with local feature descriptors and image cut-outs. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper introduces a new descriptor trained on datasets. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is possible as the descriptor is evaluated on matching benchmarks. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is possible as the paper deals with image datasets and patches. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses a semiautomatic method for generating patches.
